    Write-Centered "║              ██      ██  ██  ██  ██  ██  ██  ██      ██  ██                ║" Yellow
    Write-Centered "║              ██  ██  ██  ██  ██  ██  ██████  █████   ██  ██                ║" Yellow
    Write-Centered "║              ██  ██  ██  ██  ██  ██  ██      ██      ██  ██                ║" Yellow
    Write-Centered "║              ██████  ██████  ██████  ██      ██      ██████                ║" Yellow
